<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4">OpenAI offers $5 in free credits to new users, cached reads at $0.01/1M tokens, and volume discounts at higher tiers.</p>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">How Competitors Stack Up Today</h2>
<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4">The price gap between OpenAI and alternatives has widened significantly in 2026:</p>
<div class="overflow-x-auto my-6"><table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200 border border-gray-200"><thead><tr><th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 border-b">Provider</th><th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 border-b">Best Model</th><th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 border-b">Input</th><th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 border-b">Output</th><th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 border-b">Speed</th></tr></thead><tbody>
