<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4">Here's a Python pattern that implements a simple fallback chain, trying cheaper providers first:</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">import os, requests

def call_llm(prompt, model="deepseek-chat"):
    """Multi-provider fallback: cheap first, expensive fallback."""
